1. User types "test" → onChange runs, `setIsSearching(true)`, debounced `handleSearch` queued
2. Before debounce fires, React re-renders. The useEffect sees `isSearching=true`, skips.
3. Debounce fires → callback runs → `setFocusIndex(index)` → `setIsSearching(false)`
